{"title": "Trump levels extraordinary threat to 'fight' GOP right wing in 2018 elections", "url": "http://www.chicagotribune.com/la-na-essential-washington-updates-donald-trump-to-hard-right-republican-1490881371-htmlstory.html", "text": "President Trump lobbed an electoral threat against hard right members of his party Thursday, saying on Twitter that he would fight them in the 2018 election if they did not \"get on the team.\"\n\nThe Freedom Caucus salvo came less than a week after the group of about 30 Republican House members was blamed for derailing the GOP healthcare bill, despite efforts from Trump to negotiate with them.\n\nTrump had previously made electoral threats to wayward members of his party, but Thursday's tweet was especially direct, threatening to cast them in the same light as Democrats.", "source": "chicagotribune.com", "publish_date": "2017-03-31", "authors": "Noah Bierman", "type": "article"}